title: Ep. 394 - A Historic And Irrelevant Day
description:
Trump was impeached but nobody will care come election time. Also, a comedian brags about her abortion, claiming it made her feel "powerful." We'll talk about how we know she's lying. And is it finally time to stop making Star Wars movies? (Yes.)
